Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:20.26,OPC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}果熟落地　歸於塵土
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:23.18,OPC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you 就連傷痛
